subtitleNullable: Wine quality for red and white wine
descriptionNullable:
### Content

The two datasets are related to red and white variants of the Portuguese "Vinho Verde" wine. These datasets can be viewed as classification or regression tasks. Their are 12 attributes and used for classification or regression. 

Also check out my notebook that goes with this dataset: [Wine quality - Regression prediction](https://www.kaggle.com/brendan45774/wine-quality-regression-prediction)

### Acknowledgements
Credit goes to https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/machine-learning-databases/wine-quality/
